{"tid":1755321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理訴］區選舞弊投訴信集中區","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T17:13:58.000Z","uid":57018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f28057e9a48d20deaf11914d2a718fbc95e31806","tid":1755321,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">請大家幫幫手，啲貼實在太多太亂。<br />\n要盡快係72小時內投訴，<br />\n唔係嘅話件事就會丟淡，<br />\n請冇出尖沙咀又冇乜事做嘅手足，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊整合下以下資訊：<br />\n<br />\n1. 疑似舞弊地區（包括該區候選人）<br />\n2. 疑似舞弊模式（區區問題可能唔同，有時間改埋範本先上傳係最好！）<br />\n3. 一次過講埋有幾危急，連文宣圖都ok ar！</span><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家！"},{"pid":"2f320d6c92acb86166b147abcb91708a0340f151","tid":1755321,"uid":342055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"香港人 投訴！"},{"pid":"f6c3460e8a00fd7d29cf8918c9729186f10abbec","tid":1755321,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fd0247569857b71450c7c7aa3370ca9a4caa7a","tid":1755321,"uid":62660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"屏山北！"},{"pid":"cbb126d6aac7c1eda7aa6e791f826573fd4cdaa6","tid":1755321,"uid":164671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f320d6c92acb86166b147abcb91708a0340f151","tid":1755321,"uid":342055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"香港人 投訴！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"你個p牌仔想帶風向？"},{"pid":"ddb8f18b8167d3192b169aad6d860af75bf18510","tid":1755321,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e05897f8fa66bd6dfd03adc8695effd21e5859f","tid":1755321,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64fd0247569857b71450c7c7aa3370c